free_txt: Errors in the absolute cross section values
The targets were prepared by vacuum evaporation of
lanthanum oxides (La2O3). To get a good resolution,
the thickness of the target was limited to about 150
mu-g/cm2, evaporated onto 25 mu-g/cm2 carbon backings.
